Remove node files:
- sudo rm -rf /usr/local/{lib/node{,/.npm,_modules},bin,share/man}/{npm*,node*,man1/node*} and 
- sudo rm -rf /opt/local/bin/node /opt/local/include/node /opt/local/lib/node_modules

- NodeJS Is single threaded
- It is known for multi tasking and avoids block.


